Package: penppml
Title: Penalized Poisson Pseudo Maximum Likelihood
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Diego",
           family = "Ferreras Garrucho",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "d.ferreras-garrucho@lse.ac.uk")
Description: A package that enables estimation of penalized Poisson Pseudo Maximum Likelihood regressions,
    using lasso or ridge penalties, for models that feature high-dimensional fixed effects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
